@title LP Burner
@notice Converts Mobius LP tokens to a single asset and forwards to another burner

__init__(address,address,address).details: Unlike other burners, this contract may transfer tokens to multiple addresses after the swap. Receiver addresses are set by calling `set_swap_data` instead of setting it within the constructor.

params._emergency_owner: Emergency owner address. Can kill the contract and recover tokens.
params._owner: Owner address. Can kill the contract, recover tokens and modify the recovery address.
